{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kas to Ausi trr dehſtijs/ \nka ne buhtu tas dsirdejs? kas to\nAzzi padarrijs/ ka ne buhtu tas\nredſejs?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kas tohs Pagarus pahr-\nmahza / ne buhtu tas fohdtijs?\ntas kas teem Zilwekeen mahza to\nAtſihſchanu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS finna to\nZilweku Dohmas/ ka tahs nelee-\ntigas irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Swehtigs irr tas Wihrs\nak KUNGS! ko tu pahrmahzt/\nun kam tu tawu Bauſlibu mahzi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ka tas pazectijs effus tas KUNGS muhsu Deews\neekſch Behdu Liiſceim / teekans tohs iſdeldehs.\ntam Besdeewigam ta Bedre\ntohp iſrakta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tas KUNGS tawus\nLaudis ne atſtahs/ un fawu ee-\nmantojamu Teeju ne pamettihs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo ta Teefa atkat ees\nTaiſniba/ un tat wiſſi Sirds-\nSkaidree pakkatdsihſees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Knzch pahrſtahwehs man-\nni prett teim Blehdigeem? un\nkas stahwehs man klaht prett\nteem Launadarritajeem?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ja tas KUNGS man\npar Paligu ne buhtu/ tad man-\nna Dwehfele gann drihs buhtu\nKluſſuma gullejſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad es fazzijn: Manna\nKahja irr ſtraipalejſi / tad ak\nKUNGS! tawa Schehlaſtiba\nmann uſturreja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Man bij dauds (behdi-\ngas) Dohmas manna Sirdi/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Woj tu warretu Beedri-\nbu turreht ar to Blehdneeku\nKrehſla? kas Blehnus to ihſenu\nLikumu Weeta iſdohma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee fapulzejahs prett ta\nTaitna Dwehfeli / un paſuddi-\nna nenoseedsigu Ahini.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet tas KUNGS irr\nman par Patwerumu/ un mans\nDeews irr man par Gelbefcha-\nnas Paglahbjumu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas atmaſſahs teem\nwinnu Noseegumu/ un iſdeldehs\ntohs eekſch winnu Blehdivas /\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "bet tawas Eepreezinaschanaaß ee-\nlihgſinoja mannu Dwehfeli.\n"
    }
  ],
